WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000 line:28 position:5% align:start
How to make matcha the <b>Japanese</b> way!

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000 line:28 position:5% align:start
First, soak the whisk into warm water to soften the bristles

3
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:13.000 line:28 position:5% align:start
Then add one scoop of matcha powder and push it through a sieve gently

4
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:22.000 line:28 position:5% align:start
Add only 70mL of warm water to the matcha powder and then froth the matcha

5
00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.000 line:28 position:5% align:start
Serve the matcha in your favourite cup :D